text: Abdus Sawar is a Jatiya Party (Ershad) politician and the former Member of Parliament of Jhenaidah-4. ==Career== Sawar was elected to parliament from Jhenaidah-4 as a Jatiya Party candidate in 1986. ==References== Category:Jatiya Party politicians Category:Living people Category:3rd Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Abdus Sattar (Jhenaidah politician)
